title: Britax B Safe 35 Elite Infant Car Seat Product Video
description: Superior safety, comfort and convenience make the B-Safe 35 Elite the ideal infant car seat. SafeCell Impact Protection surrounds your child in safety and advanced layers of protection from Complete Side Impact Protection PLUS absorb crash forces and keep your child’s head and neck secure. Installation is easy with SafeCenter LATCH Installation and our Quick-Adjust Harness grows with your baby to ensure the best fit.

transcripts: Britax the leader in safety technology designed to b-safe 35 elite infant car seat to deliver advanced levels of protection for your baby. Featuring safe cell complete side impact protection plus it includes an energy absorbing head restraint to keep your baby's head and neck an extra secure on the road ahead. With our exclusive safe cell impact protection an integrated system of safety components work together to protect your baby well beyond the federal safety standards. Install with confidence using the one hand spring assisted recline and dual level indicators to make sure the infant car seat angle is correct. The safe center latch installation system uses the e.z center pull straps that cinched down securely and stow away neatly within the base. The quick adjust harness and energy absorbing head restraint grow taller with your child at the push of a button ensuring the proper fit without needing to rethread the harness straps and the removable infant insert positions even the smallest baby for a safe ride home. The click and go system featuring a quick release handle makes it easy to transfer the b-safe 35 elite to any Britax stroller. A simple click lets you know that your child's car seat is securely attached and the same quick release handle releases from the stroller back to the base. The b-safe 35 elite also features and easy remove cover that pulls right off for convenient cleaning. And premium fabrics with plush foam padding for superior comfort from the leader in safety technology. The Britax b-safe 35 elite offers the ultimate in infant car seat protection and mobility surrounding your baby and safety on the road ahead.
